<plot>Ambros, an executive who works hard for a company in Barcelona, Spain, see how his best friend and companion at work dies because heart attack in the enterprise's garage. Since then, he begin to suffer several mental problems. Someday, he decides to leave to work forever. His wife, Cecilia, played by Fiorella Faltoyano, worried about the bankruptcy for her and their sons and daughters, tries to convince him to get the job again. However, Ambros, played by Juan Luis Galiardo,thinks it's better to see his pretty wife working as a prostitute than to return to his job in the company.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?306432</url></doc>
